The protest nye triggered by the arrest of asiɛkɛ dɔwɔlawo of the hã ame ka wonye sedzidala of blocking the mɔ yi the tɔnye eme gbeɖeɖe yi bia nyo wu le dɔwɔm nɔnɔme .
The metsonu nye a siwo kplɔ wo nɔewo ɖo of interlocking events , ɖe sia ɖe ɖeka revealing the esi kplᴐe ɖo eme a si yina gagbɔna of events nu ma ends kple the ku of ɖeka of the characters .
At the yameʋudzeƒe , Nye kpᴐe e sesẽ yi xᴐe se nu ma nye nᴐvi nyᴐnu , ame ka enye nye ɖevi kple dze tugbe , would li fifia nyi fe ga yi amewo yi yi to eme kple the adzodamɔnu .
Sorani ( 2006 ) si me wo he the Hertzberg ( 1964 ) eve - memanu kpɔɖeŋu yi dometᴐ nye a eve - memanu nɔnɔme of eme nuwo kple nuteƒekpɔkpɔ .
Happily , afi ma enye geɖewo abunɛ nuwo yi enye vɔ̃ of , kple geɖewo wᴐ nuku teƒewo yi yi , gake ʋee nuwo tsɔe sɔ yi the seselelãme of nu gbagbe vɔ̃ eme a yɛye teƒe .
Transitions enye often the teƒe afi ka mí di e easiest yi blewu anyi kple tsɔ a breather .
Memlɛɖa 's nudzᴐdzᴐ nye the gbã of ene rounds of the championship nu ka determines the winner of the Formula 1 drivers ' championship .
Happy accidents dzɔ , gake the gawu commonplace the sadder the nyateƒe enye nu ma kekiake skiers lɔlɔ̃nu mlᴐeba nugbegblẽ woƒe skis .
The nᴐ anyi didi gbekui for geɖewo birds of xeƒonu ƒe nuɖuɖu enye a nesting teƒe kple no akpa tso kpᴐ .
St. Petersburg enye a delightful teƒe yi sasrã for a didi kɔsiɖanuwuwu , kple geɖewo attractions yi le aɖe asi visitors le dɔ wɔm for geɖe days .
Scientists enye eme kᴐ le edim eme finding a zã for nu sia oddly - shaped molecule , esi wònye e dze abe yi le esi geɖewo to vovo functions eme the gaxɔ .
